casebody.data:
Shadrick CHAPARRO, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
The STATE of Florida, Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D18-1735 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. OCTOBER 01, 2018 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and SALTER and LOGUE, JJ., concur.

Following review of the petition for writ of prohibition, and the response and reply thereto, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied on the merits.
